 \centering
 \includegraphics[width=\textwidth]{figures/method.jpg}
 \caption{Overview of IG-Search. \textbf{Right:} The policy model generates $G$ trajectories per question, each scored by rule-based rewards and step-level IG rewards to compute group advantages. \textbf{Left:} IG computation for search step $t$: the log-probability of the gold answer under the real retrieval context minus the average under $N$ randomly sampled retrieval contexts.}
