\paragraph{Overly Deferential Ceding}
\textbf{Scheme:} The system incorrectly treats a user's supportive backchannel as a full interruption attempt and unnecessarily cedes the floor. The generation process modifies a smooth dialogue to precisely stage this failure, as guided by the prompt in Figure~\ref{fig:prompt_deferential}, with an example in Figure~\ref{fig:json_deferential}.
