 \caption{MAML-based Knowledge Transfer in \sysname. \ding{202} Task Partitioning groups queries by policy. \ding{203} Policy Evaluator selects the best policy. \ding{204} Inner loop learns task-specific models; outer loop refines shared initialization across tasks.}\label{fig:knowledge_transfer}

